entries.title: Saving the UserId as an Int
entries.entryText: Alright so far so good. But you need to make sure that the data is sent in the right type. Which is what this test is for.

entries.title: Here's a test for the Details
entries.entryText: We're about to SEE what happens when we use some rich text, I expect this to look pretty janky. But HEY you have to try. Yah YEET
